#  Meta-Analysis Script

A comprehensive R script for conducting publication-ready meta-analyses with advanced features including sensitivity analysis, publication bias assessment, and enhanced visualizations.

![R](https://img.shields.io/badge/R-4.0%2B-blue)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green)
![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-3.2-orange)

## ðŸŒŸ Features

- **Comprehensive Meta-Analysis**: Both fixed and random effects models
- **Enhanced Visualizations**: Forest plots, funnel plots with Egger's test
- **Sensitivity Analysis**: Leave-one-out analysis, outlier detection, influence diagnostics
- **Publication Bias Assessment**: Egger's test with multiple visualization methods
- **CSV Export**: Complete results export for further analysis
- **Error Handling**: Robust error handling and multiple fallback methods
- **Sample Data Support**: Built-in sample data generation for testing

